metadata.name: are you having Fun?
metadata.description:
"are you having Fun?" is the first piece in my newest collection "ABRdFiles." This picture was the product of incredible luck; it wasn't until I'd received the scans back from processing that I saw a seagull had flown across the frame when the picture was taken. 

ABRDFiles is an homage to my time abroad in Copenhagen thus far. 

Shot on Ultramax 400.
